00:20:06,460 --> 00:20:07,160
- This way.
- Let's go.

304
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:07,680
Hurry up!

305
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:08,559
Thank you.

306
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,420
Come no.

307
00:20:09,420 --> 00:20:10,079
Cooperate with us.

308
00:20:10,599 --> 00:20:11,400
Back up.

309
00:20:11,539 --> 00:20:12,160
Jing.

310
00:20:13,099 --> 00:20:15,000
Zhou, Chen Yi's still inside!

311
00:20:15,279 --> 00:20:15,640
Come with me.

312
00:20:15,819 --> 00:20:17,319
Zhou, Chen Yi's still inside!

313
00:20:17,319 --> 00:20:17,819
Jing, come here.

314
00:20:17,819 --> 00:20:18,279
- Listen to me.
- Go

315
00:20:18,279 --> 00:20:18,759
get him out.

316
00:20:18,759 --> 00:20:19,519
Don't be reckless.

317
00:20:19,519 --> 00:20:19,920
Kang'an...

318
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,099
Please, come here.

319
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:22,559
Listen,

320
00:20:22,559 --> 00:20:23,180
calm down.

321
00:20:23,819 --> 00:20:24,740
Chen Yi's still trapped!

322
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:25,519
Leave it to the police.

323
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,359
Let us handle it.

324
00:20:26,759 --> 00:20:27,299
Don't do anything stupid.

325
00:20:42,019 --> 00:20:42,859
Go, move in!

326
00:20:43,819 --> 00:20:44,240
Hurry!

327
00:20:44,339 --> 00:20:45,279
Chen Yi!

328
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,359
- Chen Yi!
- Calm down!

329
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:46,779
Jing!

330
00:20:46,859 --> 00:20:47,559
I have to save him!

331
00:20:47,559 --> 00:20:48,759
Please, Jing!

332
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,059
Calm down!

333
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:51,400
Chen Yi!

334
00:20:51,579 --> 00:20:52,380
Stay calm.

335
00:21:22,059 --> 00:21:22,819
Next of kin?

336
00:21:22,819 --> 00:21:23,680
Where's the family?

337
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:24,779
Chen Yi!

338
00:21:25,359 --> 00:21:25,940
Chen Yi!

339
00:21:26,799 --> 00:21:27,619
- Chen Yi!
- Chen Yi!

340
00:21:33,619 --> 00:21:34,180
Chen Yi!

341
00:21:36,039 --> 00:21:36,599
Chen Yi!

342
00:22:27,259 --> 00:22:28,779
Wen! Wen!

343
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:30,720
Wen!

344
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:53,440
Hello?

345
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:56,240
We just extracted from the fire.

346
00:22:56,740 --> 00:22:58,319
Patient is a young male.

347
00:22:58,619 --> 00:22:59,400
Minor burns,

348
00:22:59,859 --> 00:23:01,160
suspected acute lung injury

349
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:01,960
from smoke inhalation.

350
00:23:02,799 --> 00:23:04,240
Vital signs stable for now.

351
00:23:05,900 --> 00:23:06,619
Chen Yi.

352
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:09,259
Please, wake up.

353
00:23:13,119 --> 00:23:15,039
My gaokao score came out,

354
00:23:15,859 --> 00:23:16,740
640.

355
00:23:17,619 --> 00:23:19,059
I applied to the local teachers' college.

356
00:23:19,799 --> 00:23:21,480
I'm staying in Vineton with you.

357
00:23:24,099 --> 00:23:24,940
You said

358
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:26,460
you'd check the scores with me.

359
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,240
Please wake up.

360
00:23:29,799 --> 00:23:31,460
Wake up.

361
00:23:38,599 --> 00:23:39,359
Chen Yi!

362
00:23:40,619 --> 00:23:41,339
Chen Yi!

363
00:23:42,099 --> 00:23:42,759
Chen Yi!

364
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:45,359
Chen Yi!

365
00:23:46,539 --> 00:23:47,119
Chen Yi!

366
00:23:47,119 --> 00:23:48,019
Miao Jing, I'm here.

367
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:51,619
Chen Yi!

368
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:00,920
Chen Yi!

369
00:24:01,099 --> 00:24:02,099
Don't touch me.

370
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:04,960
Easy.

371
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,640
Is the kid okay?

372
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:09,259
The kid's fine.

373
00:24:09,359 --> 00:24:09,960
The baby...

374
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:10,779
The child's hurt.

375
00:24:11,779 --> 00:24:12,220
Easy now.

376
00:24:17,420 --> 00:24:17,980
You alright?

377
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:19,259
I'm okay.

378
00:24:21,299 --> 00:24:22,200
Are you hurt?

379
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:23,299
Come on, follow me.

380
00:24:23,299 --> 00:24:24,279
Walk forward.

381
00:25:08,839 --> 00:25:09,900
Why're you staring at me?

382
00:25:18,740 --> 00:25:18,980
Ow...

383
00:25:19,299 --> 00:25:19,799
that hurts.

384
00:25:19,799 --> 00:25:20,259
My hand...

385
00:25:21,079 --> 00:25:21,779
my hand's killing me.

386
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:25,680
You scared me half to death,

387
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:26,440
you know that?

388
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,259
Looks like he's fine,

389
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:03,960
still got his smart mouth.

390
00:26:06,299 --> 00:26:07,359
Brought you hot roast goose.

391
00:26:11,180 --> 00:26:12,319
Came to check on you.

392
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,039
Jing,

393
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:16,759
get me a glass of water, will you?

394
00:26:22,059 --> 00:26:22,559
Go on.

395
00:26:23,299 --> 00:26:24,259
He's not gonna bite.

396
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:39,220
Tell me,

397
00:26:40,619 --> 00:26:41,400
how'd you end up

398
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,380
banged up again?

399
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:06,119
Doctor says three more days' observation.

400
00:27:06,119 --> 00:27:07,299
Don't you dare take this lightly.

401
00:27:08,119 --> 00:27:09,279
Mess up that arm again,

402
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:10,819
and you'll feel it every rainy day

403
00:27:10,819 --> 00:27:11,619
for the rest of your life.

404
00:27:12,519 --> 00:27:13,480
It's not that bad.

405
00:27:14,819 --> 00:27:15,259
Here.

406
00:27:15,799 --> 00:27:16,440
You can't eat this yet.

407
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,319
Not till you heal up.

408
00:27:22,759 --> 00:27:23,940
So I just get to look at it?

409
00:27:24,099 --> 00:27:24,839
Here you go.

410
00:27:28,059 --> 00:27:29,180
You listen to her.

411
00:27:29,779 --> 00:27:31,240
Don't know when you've got it good.

412
00:27:32,319 --> 00:27:32,779
Rest up.

413
00:27:32,779 --> 00:27:33,440
I'm heading out.

414
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:39,319
You can't have it, but I can.

415
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:40,319
I'm taking this.

416
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:41,339
Hey...

417
00:27:47,359 --> 00:27:48,599
You only get this.

418
00:27:59,700 --> 00:28:00,380
Since he's awake,

419
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:01,279
he's out of danger.

420
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:01,839
Family should

421
00:28:01,839 --> 00:28:02,839
head home and rest.

422
00:28:03,220 --> 00:28:03,579
Got it.

423
00:28:21,319 --> 00:28:21,740
Miao Jing,

424
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,579
go home and get some sleep.

425
00:28:24,279 --> 00:28:25,259
I'll have Bo come sit with me.

426
00:28:25,559 --> 00:28:26,819
Doctor said no moving around.

427
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:29,980
What?

428
00:28:31,779 --> 00:28:33,420
I said get Bo over here.

429
00:28:33,420 --> 00:28:34,140
You go home.

430
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:35,599
I'm not hungry yet.

431
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:37,839
Miao Jing,

432
00:28:39,740 --> 00:28:40,220
be good.

433
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:42,359
You thirsty?

434
00:28:42,359 --> 00:28:43,059
Have some water.

435
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:50,660
I'm fine, up and walking.

436
00:28:50,660 --> 00:28:51,599
I really don't need you here.

437
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,480
- Afternoon, ma'am.
- Hey there.

438
00:29:37,759 --> 00:29:38,240
Nurse,

439
00:29:39,099 --> 00:29:40,079
where's the patient in this bed?

440
00:29:40,519 --> 00:29:41,140
Haven't seen him.

441
00:29:41,140 --> 00:29:42,240
Probably stepped out.

442
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:53,619
What're you doing?

443
00:29:54,839 --> 00:29:55,420
Following me

444
00:29:55,420 --> 00:29:56,079
even to the bathroom?

445
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,819
Thought you'd run off.

446
00:30:02,559 --> 00:30:03,099
Where'm I gonna go

447
00:30:03,099 --> 00:30:03,839
half banged up?

448
00:30:04,619 --> 00:30:05,200
You vanished

449
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,019
without a word

450
00:30:06,019 --> 00:30:06,779
once before.

451
00:30:06,779 --> 00:30:07,220
Who says

452
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:08,240
you won't do it again?

453
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,099
Fine.

454
00:30:13,319 --> 00:30:14,339
When I'm done,

455
00:30:14,599 --> 00:30:15,319
you can tuck me in your pocket.

456
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:21,880
Now get out.

457
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:22,440
You...

458
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:23,180
You standing there is...

459
00:30:23,559 --> 00:30:24,160
No.

460
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,220
I'll wait with you.

461
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:28,240
I can't pee with you here.

462
00:30:31,019 --> 00:30:31,660
Close the door.

463
00:30:36,119 --> 00:30:36,720
Not closing?

464
00:30:38,359 --> 00:30:38,700
Suit yourself.

465
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,940
I'll wait outside.

466
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:44,519
Hurry up.

467
00:31:14,279 --> 00:31:15,319
You asleep?

468
00:31:19,940 --> 00:31:21,180
Your blanket's slipping.

469
00:31:26,099 --> 00:31:26,500
Miao Jing,

470
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:28,940
you here to nag me

471
00:31:28,940 --> 00:31:29,759
or keep me company?

472
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:45,420
What?

473
00:31:45,579 --> 00:31:46,319
Come sleep in the bed.

474
00:31:50,799 --> 00:31:52,539
Those pain meds

475
00:31:52,539 --> 00:31:53,740
work pretty good.

476
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:55,539
You're healing fast.

477
00:32:03,019 --> 00:32:03,680
I meant

478
00:32:04,099 --> 00:32:05,140
you take the big bed,

479
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:06,200
I'll take the cot.

480
00:32:07,359 --> 00:32:08,640
You've been running around for days.

481
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,500
You need rest.

482
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:10,880
Come here.

483
00:32:13,259 --> 00:32:14,400
Then sleep together.

484
00:32:51,160 --> 00:32:51,700
You asleep?

485
00:32:55,599 --> 00:32:56,220
No.

486
00:32:57,660 --> 00:32:58,720
I was thinking.

487
00:33:03,140 --> 00:33:03,799
About what?

488
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,000
When you'll

489
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,240
stop treating me

490
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:13,759
like an outsider.

491
00:33:14,500 --> 00:33:15,880
You'd rather bother Bo

492
00:33:16,539 --> 00:33:17,460
than ask me for help.

493
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:25,619
It's not that.

494
00:33:25,619 --> 00:33:26,279
I just...

495
00:33:33,380 --> 00:33:33,900
I don't want

496
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,039
my girlfriend doing all this

497
00:33:36,579 --> 00:33:37,460
like it's expected.

498
00:33:51,319 --> 00:33:51,940
Chen Yi,

499
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:55,740
we've got our whole lives

500
00:33:55,740 --> 00:33:56,740
ahead of us.

501
00:33:57,799 --> 00:33:59,039
When we're old,

502
00:34:00,279 --> 00:34:01,900
I'll be leaning on you,

503
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,359
and you'll be leaning on me.

504
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,300
We're family.

505
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:50,980
You two didn't have to come.

506
00:34:51,559 --> 00:34:52,400
The pool hall

507
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,460
must be swamped.

508
00:34:53,679 --> 00:34:54,400
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.

509
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,380
My arm's almost better.

510
00:34:55,380 --> 00:34:56,360
No need for all this.

511
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:57,679
Get well soon.

512
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:00,179
Here, Mid-Autumn gift.

513
00:35:00,179 --> 00:35:00,920
Alright, got to go.

514
00:35:01,619 --> 00:35:02,460
Take it easy

515
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:03,579
now you're discharged.

516
00:35:03,579 --> 00:35:04,400
Don't overdo it.

517
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:04,880
Got it.

518
00:35:05,099 --> 00:35:05,420
- Thanks.
- Here.

519
00:35:05,420 --> 00:35:05,980
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.

520
00:35:17,260 --> 00:35:18,099
All set.

521
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:25,480
What's this?

522
00:35:33,519 --> 00:35:34,960
Come on, let's go home.

523
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:13,980
Miao Jing, grab a piece of cardboard.

524
00:36:15,599 --> 00:36:16,599
A piece of cardboard.

525
00:36:21,719 --> 00:36:22,739
This is all we have.

526
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:24,360
Fine.

527
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,840
That looks so messy.

528
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:36,659
Ditching the cigarettes?

529
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:37,860
They got damp.

530
00:36:38,079 --> 00:36:39,420
Haven't touched 'em since we got back.

531
00:36:40,079 --> 00:36:40,960
Being good, huh?

532
00:36:52,199 --> 00:36:53,440
That mooncake's huge.

533
00:36:56,219 --> 00:36:57,360
We'll eat it after the offering.

534
00:36:57,719 --> 00:36:58,539
We'll never finish it.

535
00:37:00,059 --> 00:37:00,920
With you around? Please.

536
00:37:01,579 --> 00:37:02,860
I don't eat that much.

537
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:25,079
What'd you wish for

538
00:37:25,079 --> 00:37:25,800
that took so long?

539
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:27,159
Just one thing.

540
00:37:28,039 --> 00:37:28,500
What?

541
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:32,320
Won't come true if I say it.

542
00:37:33,099 --> 00:37:34,059
Stingy.

543
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,420
Haven't seen you

544
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:07,280
wear those earrings in forever.

545
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:10,599
Nice?

546
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:13,840
Matches your necklace.

547
00:38:16,559 --> 00:38:17,219
You like them?

548
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,599
They look good.

549
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:31,119
Well,

550
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:32,500
tell me

551
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:33,639
your wish,

552
00:38:34,699 --> 00:38:36,059
and I'll kiss you in them.

553
00:38:42,019 --> 00:38:42,800
I want...

554
00:38:43,519 --> 00:38:44,179
Want what?

555
00:38:49,519 --> 00:38:49,980
To always

556
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:51,360
be right here with you.

557
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:05,260
Still hurt?

558
00:40:07,940 --> 00:40:08,739
Stopped hurting ages ago.

559
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,300
Before they took me to Jinguo,

560
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,300
Zhai Fengmao tied me up at the docks.

561
00:40:26,179 --> 00:40:26,960
Truth is,

562
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:29,820
I wasn't scared.

563
00:40:32,699 --> 00:40:33,780
I just kept thinking...

564
00:40:37,159 --> 00:40:38,500
I never got to say a proper goodbye.

565
00:40:41,159 --> 00:40:42,320
Never got to

566
00:40:44,239 --> 00:40:45,480
hold your hand like this.

567
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:02,840
Chen Yi.

568
00:41:05,619 --> 00:41:06,460
You're mine.

569
00:42:06,599 --> 00:42:07,139
Good morning.

570
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:08,860
Morning.

571
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,480
Breakfast's on the table.

572
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:22,519
What?

573
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:25,340
You woke up before I could even say

574
00:42:25,340 --> 00:42:26,059
good morning.

575
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:29,000
So?

576
00:42:29,820 --> 00:42:30,719
Nothing.

577
00:42:38,500 --> 00:42:39,679
That stings.

578
00:42:41,159 --> 00:42:42,019
Haven't shaved.

579
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:43,280
Then shave.

580
00:42:45,940 --> 00:42:46,460
Move.

581
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:57,420
Let me do it.

582
00:42:59,179 --> 00:43:00,300
You know how?

583
00:43:11,860 --> 00:43:12,420
Like this?

584
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:17,219
Easy.

585
00:43:18,099 --> 00:43:18,699
Lower.

586
00:43:24,159 --> 00:43:25,159
Don't move.

587
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:31,119
Lower still.

588
00:43:32,980 --> 00:43:34,199
Bad angle.

589
00:43:44,980 --> 00:43:46,019
Lower.

590
00:43:48,239 --> 00:43:48,860
What're you doing?

591
00:43:56,000 --> 00:43:56,960
Low enough for you?

592
00:43:58,300 --> 00:43:58,820
Perfect.

593
00:44:02,500 --> 00:44:03,639
For the record,

594
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:05,960
the fire

595
00:44:05,960 --> 00:44:07,300
wasn't an accident.

596
00:44:08,579 --> 00:44:09,320
They used it

597
00:44:09,320 --> 00:44:10,840
to draw

598
00:44:11,460 --> 00:44:13,000
everyone's attention.

599
00:44:17,760 --> 00:44:18,980
And here I thought you were gonna say

600
00:44:18,980 --> 00:44:19,780
something sweet.

601
00:44:22,039 --> 00:44:23,480
They're rushing.

602
00:44:23,539 --> 00:44:24,880
They'll slip up.

603
00:44:25,099 --> 00:44:25,780
So,

